msgid "Sync check"
msgstr "Sünki kontroll"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:705
msgid "The room was not quiet enough to verify — pause other audio and calibrate once more."
msgstr "Tuba ei olnud kontrolliks piisavalt vaikne — peata muu heli ja kalibreeri veel kord."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:733
msgid "%1 stayed silent through both rounds — it was left out of the group. Tick it back in the speaker list any time."
msgstr "%1 püsis mõlemas voorus vait — see jäeti grupist välja. Linnukesega kõlarite nimekirjas saad ta igal hetkel tagasi."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:738
msgid "%1 made no sound the microphone could hear. If it stays silent on the next calibration too, it will be left out of the group."
msgstr "%1 ei teinud ühtegi heli, mida mikrofon kuuleks. Kui ta jääb vait ka järgmisel kalibreerimisel, jäetakse ta grupist välja."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:745
msgid "Could not hear %1 during the check — the speaker may be muted or off. The calibration was kept."
msgstr "Kontrolli ajal ei olnud %1 kuulda — kõlar võib olla vaigistatud või väljas. Kalibratsioon jäi alles."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:753
msgid "Sync verified"
msgstr "Sünk kinnitatud"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:754
msgid "Every speaker arrives within %1 ms at the microphone — in step to the ear."
msgstr "Iga kõlar jõuab mikrofonini %1 ms sees — kõrva jaoks ühes taktis."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:758
msgid "The speakers still arrive %1 ms apart. Calibrate once more, or nudge the delay slider."
msgstr "Kõlarid saabuvad endiselt %1 ms vahega. Kalibreeri veel kord või nihuta viite liugurit."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1385
msgid "Two rounds of clicks with a quiet check between them — about two minutes in total. The music stays silent until the check finishes."
msgstr "Kaks klõpsuvooru, nende vahel vaikne kontroll — kokku umbes kaks minutit. Muusika püsib vait, kuni kontroll lõpeb."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1387
msgid "Skipped (empty jack): %1."
msgstr "Vahele jäetud (tühi pesa): %1."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1388
msgid "Calibration started"
msgstr "Kalibratsioon algas"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1449
msgid "All local outputs (On Air)"
msgstr "Kõik kohalikud väljundid (On Air)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:2094
msgid "%1 did not join the sync"
msgstr "%1 ei liitunud sünkrooniga"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:2096
msgid "The speaker is connected but could not be pulled into the group — switch the sync off and on to rebuild it."
msgstr "Kõlar on ühendatud, aga teda ei õnnestunud gruppi tuua — lülita sünk korraks välja ja uuesti sisse."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:2097
msgid "The speaker is connected but its audio output never appeared — switch the speaker off and on, then connect it again."
msgstr "Kõlar on ühendatud, aga selle heliväljundit ei tekkinud — lülita kõlar korraks välja ja sisse ning ühenda uuesti."

#~ msgid "Listening to the clicks…"
#~ msgstr "Kuulan klõpse…"

#~ msgid "This speaker's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device."
#~ msgstr "Selle kõlari osa helitugevusest — tasakaal järgib iga põhiliuguri liigutust ja jäetakse seadme jaoks meelde."

#~ msgid "Volume: "
#~ msgstr "Helitugevus: "

#~ msgid "Cast to"
#~ msgstr "Mängi seadmes"
